><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">]</span></span></span></span> ，求使剩余区间互不重叠所需移除区间的最小数量（仅端点重合不算重合）</p>
